{
  "stem": "14724.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My son, who didn't know what he wanted to do-- my husband was-- and now Colin was in transport, you know, with-- with one of the big car firms.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So because Martin didn't know what he wanted to do, we put him into transport with some friends of ours.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he's virtually been in it ever since.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And for someone who didn't like schooling, he was-- he went on to become transport manager by the time he was 21.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because he enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it-- it was a-- he always loved a challenge.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he-- he did very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My daughter's a teacher, has been a teacher for many a moon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they're both married to the most delightful partners.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If I would've had the choice of partners for them, I think I would've picked the ones they have.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My Martin is married to Wendy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And Anita is married to Hugh.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And Anita and Hugh have given me two wonderful grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There's Daniel, who's 18.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there's Hannah, who's 13.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that is the only thing I have to thank my first husband for.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that's for my children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Other than that, I mean-- my-- as you, I think, said, my life, my earlier life was pretty-- not much of a life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My first marriage was no life at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And just work and work and work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we-- we-- I had to originally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because before the-- my-- Colin's wife would divorce him, we had to keep her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to do that, I had to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I've been an arthritic for 30-odd years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had to come away from the garage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because that's all out in the open.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I went and I ran what we call an estate agent's office.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which you call Realtors?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Real estate.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
